headline: Boston Beer (SAM) Soars 4.6%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: Boston Beer (SAM) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
